## User stories

- Bronze

*As a user I want to be able to view blogs so that I can view information
* As a user I want to be able to search for blogs about certain cities so I can visit reccomended activies near me 

- Silver
* As a user I want to be able to create blogs to add to the main board

-Gold
* As a user I want to be able to edit/update my blogs so I can maintain their significance
* As a user I want to be able to delete blogs so that I can resolve errors
* As a user I want to be able to log in securely to my profile so that I can complete the above two functions

